{"tid":1178723,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人唔中意同朋友成日見","createTime":"2019-05-30T15:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T16:58:06.000Z","uid":161743,"like":22,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9f3da96805fa9d2f1f5b074f5eb69e7cc3c4f0df","tid":1178723,"uid":161743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:11:22.000Z","msg":"中學畢業左5年 班中學朋友話要一個月最少聚一次<br />\n你哋次次出嚟食嘢又唔係平 平野又話唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實有冇人同我一樣都唔鍾意同朋友見得咁密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反而中意幾個月到半年先聚一聚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/41UZW6H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F41UZW6H.png&h=82e4164e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c652b1bff9826010d1d700dc98b8ea28bdcb04c","tid":1178723,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"同女朋友成日見就鍾意姐"},{"pid":"d689d5806c5e1a5b92ab749ec7a63df87289b8c6","tid":1178723,"uid":8500,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:13:17.000Z","msg":"一個月一次都縑多<br />\n果一陣真係可以每個人都講到成個月想分享既野咩"},{"pid":"0197be61fc84e2a7cee7db3d8e34b7ddb053931f","tid":1178723,"uid":100772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:14:26.000Z","msg":"通常畢業後就唔再見"},{"pid":"da449d7aac6cc1aac99fa92114b3236d11a114e3","tid":1178723,"uid":161743,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0197be61fc84e2a7cee7db3d8e34b7ddb053931f","tid":1178723,"uid":100772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:14:26.000Z","msg":"通常畢業後就唔再見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:16:41.000Z","msg":"全部舊朋友都冇再keep？"},{"pid":"9154b0a5e7568ae5bfc93fbcf7428e49cf860840","tid":1178723,"uid":248336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c652b1bff9826010d1d700dc98b8ea28bdcb04c","tid":1178723,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"同女朋友成日見就鍾意姐"},"citedBy":0,